{"tid":987392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【屯門大欖貨倉爆炸】現場流出紅色液體　河水染紅","createTime":"2019-01-19T09:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T17:03:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"55a14c0474ac58ffbfc051e419b2dbf2e51e5d0a","tid":987392,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190119/s00001/f5fd9f4ef8ef035a1b0ab6514f17ae99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190119%2Fs00001%2Ff5fd9f4ef8ef035a1b0ab6514f17ae99.jpg&h=adcc26ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【17:20更新】火警發生後，現場貨倉不斷流出無味的紅色液體，附近河道及地面被染成一片紅色，紅色液體沿大欖涌河流入大欖水警基地對開海面。<br />\n<br />\n【09:49】凌晨1時40分，屯門大欖涌路110號一個物流貨倉發生火警及冒出濃煙，其間傳出多次爆炸聲，消防員接報到場開三條喉及出動三隊煙帽隊撲救，至凌晨4時14分將火救熄。火警中無人受傷亦毋須疏散。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，火場面積達150米乘30米，貨倉由鋅鐵搭蓋而成，面積約8萬平方呎，火警中有大量布匹、玩具及雜貨等被焚毀，7架貨櫃車被波及。消防經初步調查後，認為起火原因無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190119/s00001/1547861871841/【屯門大欖貨倉爆炸】現場流出紅色液體-河水染紅\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190119%2Fs00001%2F1547861871841%2F%E3%80%90%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%A4%A7%E6%AC%96%E8%B2%A8%E5%80%89%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E3%80%91%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E6%B5%81%E5%87%BA%E7%B4%85%E8%89%B2%E6%B6%B2%E9%AB%94-%E6%B2%B3%E6%B0%B4%E6%9F%93%E7%B4%85&d=BzfQOgOuAR39WBJe82ZQjdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=c5350ac2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190119%2Fs00001%2F1547861871841%2F%E3%80%90%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%A4%A7%E6%AC%96%E8%B2%A8%E5%80%89%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E3%80%91%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E6%B5%81%E5%87%BA%E7%B4%85%E8%89%B2%E6%B6%B2%E9%AB%94-%E6%B2%B3%E6%B0%B4%E6%9F%93%E7%B4%85&h=9db7ef30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190119/s00001/1547861871841/【屯門大欖貨倉爆炸】現場流出紅色液體-河水染紅</a>"},{"pid":"5c4177a2c477841737ac5e84d85419701